{"tid":337620,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[耶撚勿入]聖經真相","createTime":"2017-07-27T12:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T15:45:44.000Z","uid":25161,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5aeef70ca8cbaffc94f2a370ffb591b63ec236a2","tid":337620,"uid":25161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"第一章：耶穌由來<br />\n話說約瑟個仔個老豆阿約瑟佢呢<br />\n就從來無同耶穌個老母瑪利亞扑野既<br />\n咁呀穌哥係點黎架呢<br />\n<br />\n有一日.約瑟返到屋企發現瑪利亞大左肚<br />\n咁無扑野又點會大肚 約瑟都心知不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呢一刻 瑪利亞竟然同約瑟講 <br />\n個肚入面果個係耶穌 係聖靈感感孕<br />\n叫做耶穌 佢係要黎拯救呢個世界 <br />\n係上帝派落黎既使者<br />\n你估約瑟信唔信 我估佢唔信 <br />\n之後就係真正既開始<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人只是在學生生涯接觸過聖經 並無只細研究過 所以對於聖經既知識好少"},{"pid":"ee68a39e0f2a46dc1a95ed6c945335646198b0fd","tid":337620,"uid":19967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fcc5a21a6893ef5aab5f956d0b11d7ece3bfe2","tid":337620,"uid":125553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"講緊乜撚嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}